    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i just cant do this anymore. the nerve pain is so constant it feels like my whole body is on fire 24/7 and there's no end in sight. i'm just so tired of fighting for a life that feels like nothing but a cycle of agony. sometimes it feels like the only actual way to get some peace is just... to not be here. like, wouldn't it be a mercy to just stop the noise?",
